articles.title: Sarah Burton and Alexander McQueen to part ways after more than two decades - Vogue Business
articles.description: Creative director Sarah Burton and the Kering-owned fashion house have announced the end of their collaboration. The upcoming Spring/Summer 2024 show in Paris “will mark the conclusion of a highly successful partnership”, they said in a statement on Monday.
